• Using advanced turbocharging and direct injection systems; 
• Adding exhaust gas recirculation (EGR) to reduce oxygen levels and thus nitrogen oxide (NOx) emissions; 
• Installing particulate filters to reduce soot emissions; 
• Utilizing electric or hybrid propulsion systems; 
